{"tid":1828484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"悍匪頭目季炳強清晨被送美","createTime":"2020-01-18T01:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T15:18:45.000Z","uid":230104,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"589eaf15a6521d1678927c657639e73e12e831e9","tid":1828484,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:37:31.000Z","msg":"由於現年59歲的季炳雄被懷疑與多宗開槍傷人械劫集團有聯繫，對於季炳雄今日出獄一事，警方以最高保安規格方式處理，並會出動飛虎隊戒備。消息人士稱，當局一方面要確保沒有香港居留權的季炳雄，出獄後立即「遣送」美國，不會在香港機場或其他地方不知所終；但另一方面，季出獄後卻已是無罪之身，當局難以手銬或其他方式強逼他上機，故只能由他出獄一刻開始「護送」他直接抵達機場禁區。據悉，今日清晨季炳雄出獄後，會立即由懲教人員陪同上車直達機場，飛虎隊不會上車，但會在旁組成車隊沿途監視及保護。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LpHNYOH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpHNYOH.jpg&h=8805e56b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c895d7bb7e52dc591ab00ced2401ca1e98386189","tid":1828484,"uid":511,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:40:33.000Z","msg":"做咩幫佢著制服又載埋帽嘅？"},{"pid":"238055050898a69b585cd5b0bf022615c7752080","tid":1828484,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:44:45.000Z","msg":"一路順風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83f1825277793bbdcbe66b9e17eac97e0913d9c","tid":1828484,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c895d7bb7e52dc591ab00ced2401ca1e98386189","tid":1828484,"uid":511,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:40:33.000Z","msg":"做咩幫佢著制服又載埋帽嘅？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:45:11.000Z","msg":"程序之一"},{"pid":"7d0fdbfac4a17537bb8644a0404966ee28e1408b","tid":1828484,"uid":241512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:47:18.000Z","msg":"頭號通緝犯都去到美國 點解振美唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e31dd797066f08ca132edd34cd24f70b2bfa2c1","tid":1828484,"uid":93649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:50:08.000Z","msg":"早機去 夜機番香港"},{"pid":"39220685cf5232d6